# WorkEaseHub 🛠️

**WorkEaseHub** is a full-stack project built to practice and demonstrate my skills across both front-end and back-end development. This project showcases modern web development techniques, clean code practices, and a complete workflow from development to deployment.

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

### 💻 Front-End
- HTML
- CSS / SASS
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- TypeScript
- DOM Manipulation
- Webpack

### 🧠 Back-End
- Node.js
- MongoDB
- REST APIs

### 🛠️ Tools & DevOps
- Git & GitHub
- ESLint
- Docker
- Postman
- Vercel (Deployment)
- Visual Studio Code
- Jira (Task Management)

---

## 📦 Features

- Responsive UI with modern styling
- Dynamic DOM interactions
- API integration with RESTful endpoints
- MongoDB for data storage and retrieval
- Linted and modular codebase using ESLint
- Deployed on Vercel with CI/CD
- Dockerized for consistency across environments

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/noureba/WorkEaseHub.git
cd workeasehub